OL,3,CScottish Government say update on D&G
OL,4,CNational Park to come next Thursday
OL,6,FAn announcement on the future of a
OL,7,Fcontroversial National Park proposal
OL,8,Fin Dumfries and Galloway will be made
OL,9,Fnext Thursday, the Scottish Government
OL,10,Fhave said.
OL,12,FAdvisory agency Nature Scot have
OL,13,Fcompiled a report on the plan, based
OL,14,Fin part on a three month long
OL,15,Fconsultation with local people and
OL,16,Fbusinesses in Galloway, which was
OL,17,Fpresented to Ministers earlier this
OL,18,Fmonth.
