OL,3,CScottish Government say update on D&G
OL,4,CNational Park to come next Thursday
OL,6,FIf Minister's green light the plan
OL,7,Fthere'll be another round of
OL,8,Fconsultation before a final decision
OL,9,Fis made. If not, it's possible the
OL,10,Fproposal could be dropped entirely.
OL,12,FHolyrood have confirmed that a
OL,13,Fstatement will be given in Parliament
OL,14,Fnext Thursday.
OL,16,FIn a statement the Rural Affairs
OL,17,FSecretary Mairi Gougeon said: "I would
OL,18,Flike to thank all those who took part
OL,19,Fin the consultation on whether there
OL,20,Fshould be a new National Park in
OL,21,FGalloway and South and East Ayrshire.
