OL,6,F"Now that we have received
OL,7,FNatureScot's report of the
OL,8,Fconsultation findings and advice on
OL,9,Fthe proposal, we have carefully
OL,10,Fconsidered these and will update
OL,11,Fparliament on Thursday on the next
OL,12,Fsteps."
OL,14,FAt the beginning of May one local MSP
OL,15,Fsaid the consultation findings,
OL,16,Fincluded in the Nature Scot report,
OL,17,Fshowed that a majority of locals did
OL,18,Fnot support the plans.
