OL,3,CScottish Government say update on D&G
OL,4,CNational Park to come next Thursday
OL,6,FSpeaking in Parliament, Finlay Carson,
OL,7,FConservative MSP for Galloway and West
OL,8,FDumfries, said: "It is my
OL,9,Funderstanding that there is not a
OL,10,Fmajority in favour of the national
OL,11,Fpark proposal and that a full
OL,12,Fdesignation order is unlikely to be
OL,13,Fmade."
OL,15,FIn response a Minister said: "The
OL,16,Frural affairs secretary has to look at
OL,17,Fthe results of the consultation and
OL,18,Ftake them seriously. An awful lot of
OL,19,Finformation is included in the
OL,20,Fconsultation, and she will advise the
OL,21,FParliament when she is ready to do so."
