OL,3,CScottish Government say update on D&G
OL,4,CNational Park to come next Thursday
OL,6,FGalloway was selected as the preferred
OL,7,Foption to become Scotland's newest
OL,8,FNational Park in July last year. Since
OL,9,Fthen, the proposal has become highly
OL,10,Fcontroversial, with a campaign group
OL,11,Fopposing the plans attracting hundreds
OL,12,Fof followers on social media and
OL,13,Fprotests held across the region.
