OL,3,CScottish Government say update on D&G
OL,4,CNational Park to come next Thursday
OL,6,FOpponents have a number of concerns
OL,7,Fabout the proposed park, suggesting
OL,8,Fthat house prices could rise, and over
OL,9,Ftourism could put pressure on local
OL,10,Finfrastructure. The National Farmers
OL,11,FUnion has also come out strongly
OL,12,Fagainst the plans which it claims
OL,13,Fwould negatively affect the faming
OL,14,Fcommunity.
OL,16,FBut those in favour believe the
OL,17,FNational Park offers a once in a
OL,18,Fgeneration opportunity for the region,
OL,19,Fwhich could attract inward investment,
OL,20,Fextra Government funding and help look
OL,21,Fafter Galloway's landscape.
